# Multiple fault dataset

Files in this directory contain the information about which bugs are included in each buggy version.

- The file `<project_name>.json.pairs.csv` lists a set of pairs `(N, M)` such that `N` is detected in `M`.
    ```csv
    N,M
    1,2
    1,3
    ...
    ```
- The file `<project_name>.json` gives which bugs (`<N1>`, ..., `<Nn>`) are contained in each buggy version `M`.
    ```json
    {   
        "<M>": {
            "<N1>": "list of fault revealing test cases",
            "<N2>": "list of fault revealing test cases",
            // ...
            "<Nn>": "list of fault revealing test cases",
        }
    }
    ```
